a table format on the serial monitor and can be useful for <a href=\"https:\/\/coert.vonk.one\/sw\/arduino\/pitch-detector\/verification-31583\">verification<\/a>.<\/li>\r\n    <\/ul>\r\n<\/p>\r\n<p>\r\n    We created the G-key as a black and white .bmp file and converted it to a C structure using <code>images\/bmp.c<\/code>.\r\n<\/p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <div class=\"continue-container no-print\">\r\n        <div class=\"continue-content\">\r\n            <div class=\"continue-text\">\r\n                With pitch detection, segmentation and visualization in place, the <a href=\"https:\/\/coert.vonk.one\/sw\/arduino\/pitch-detector\/sending-midi-events-31581\">next page<\/a> describes how MIDI events are sent to a synthesizer.\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>    \r\n<\/p>\r\n\r\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Describes visualizing the notes for pitch detection on Arduino. It gives a brief description of the visualization methods.","protected":false},"author":41,"featured_media":18417,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"categories":[433],"tags":[361,466,472],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v18.7 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Visualizing the notes for pitch detection on Arduino - Johan Vonk<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Describes visualizing the notes for pitch detection on Arduino. It gives a brief description of the visualization methods.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/coert.vonk.one\/sw\/arduino\/pitch-detector\/visualizing-the-notes-31579\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Visualizing the notes for pitch d